      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WILUNA LASS (3) trialled very sharply coming into this, showing plenty of speed to win a 400m trial, with the horse she beat running well on Saturday in stronger company. The inside draw is ideal as she'll be up front from the draw and if she can pick up from where she left off, she'll be hard to reel in. ORDER ONLINE (2) flew home to just miss over the 1000m at Ascot last time out and should be better for that performance. Turner remains in the saddle and there looks to be genuine pace in this, so it should set up nicely for him if he's within striking distance. Watch for him late in the race. DOOR BUSTER (4) has looked good at the trials coming into this and was very good when winning on debut at Northam at her only run last campaign. Can roll forward and make her presence felt. ACORN (1) comes here without a trial but has to be included on his form last campaign. SNIP OF ROMANCE (8) is next best.",
